## Blockers & Open Questions

- **ROADMAP.md terminology** — "부서" → "팀" update needed before coding starts.
- **Subframe free plan** — Limited to 3 pages. May need Pro ($29/mo) for 12 pages.
- **Claude OAuth CLI token** — CEO mentioned this for Phase 2. Confirmed NOT a current Anthropic product. Needs research.
- **Node-based UI** — CEO wants n8n/SketchVibe-style drag-and-drop for agent assignment. React Flow identified for Phase 2+.

